Market Analysis and Size

In recent years, an increasing number of gluten-free foods have appeared on supermarket shelves and been marketed directly to consumers through internet channels. As a result, several leading food companies offer gluten-free products. They also promote gluten-free prepared foods, such as oat-based cereals and crackers made from grains like oats, rice, and corn.

